&= | \mathbf{a}| | \mathbf{b} \times \mathbf{c} | cos (\theta_{ac}) \\
&= | \mathbf{a}| |\mathbf{b}||\mathbf{c}| sin (\theta_{bc}) cos (\theta_{ac}) \\
